(59, 1, '2019-03-15 01:05:52', '2019-03-15 01:05:52', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> We are experts in rejuvenating timber decking, cladding and any other external timber surface.<br>Preparation is key, so much of our emphasis is on prepping the surfaces to ensure a great result.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>Cleaning</strong>Prior to any application, it is essential that the timber has been cleaned. Our team of professionals will thoroughly clean your timber surfaces to ensure a perfect end result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>Sanding</strong>Where sanding is required, we use an industrial strength vacuum system to ensure dust is virtually eliminated.<br><strong>Oiling &amp; Staining</strong>Once the timber surfaces have been prepped, we apply your chosen finishes.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Upon completion, we do a complete clean and clear so you\'re ready to once again enjoy the beautiful rejuvenated look of your timber.<br>Check out our work </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Restoration & Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-15 01:05:52', '2019-03-15 01:05:52', '', 46, 'http://localhost:9000/?p=59', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
