(99, 1, '2019-03-25 22:07:49', '2019-03-25 22:07:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all sides of your timber are protected prior to use.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>How does it work?</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;<br>Watch how we process a typical order<em>(links</em><em> to short video)</em><br>Get a quote or place an order <em>(link</em><em> to pricing calculator)</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>\n<p></p>', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-25 22:07:49', '2019-03-25 22:07:49', '', 93, 'http://localhost:9000/?p=99', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
