(139, 2, '2019-04-24 06:38:35', '2019-04-24 06:38:35', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-Coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all six sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture and rot can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber onsite, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is Cutek - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, Cutek works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides years of protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch how we process a typical order<em> (link to short video)</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Get a quote or place an order <em>(link to pricing calculator)</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-24 06:38:35', '2019-04-24 06:38:35', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(140, 2, '2019-04-24 06:40:39', '2019-04-24 06:40:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all six sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture and rot can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber onsite, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is Cutek - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, Cutek works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides years of protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Watch how we process a typical order</strong><em> (link to short video)</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Enquire about pricing or ordering</strong> <em>(link to pricing info)</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-24 06:40:39', '2019-04-24 06:40:39', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(141, 2, '2019-04-24 21:23:21', '2019-04-24 21:23:21', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at Sydney Timber Solutions, we specialise in protecting and beautifying timber.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We love the<strong> natural look</strong> of timber; that it\'s a <strong>renewable resource</strong>; and that it can be maintained <strong>cost effectively</strong>. Most of all, we love helping our customers get the most out of their timber.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With over 20 years experience in timber restoration and applications, we are experts in protecting timber and bringing out its natural beauty. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>We Specialise In</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Pre-coating timber - so that it arrives onsite, pre-treated and ready to install.</li><li>Restoring and maintaining timber in both residential and commercial settings such as decks, cladding on houses or buildings, public walk ways, and public space furniture such as park benches</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-24 21:23:21', '2019-04-24 21:23:21', '', 7, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
