(201, 2, '2019-04-30 02:52:36', '2019-04-30 02:52:36', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> For architects, ensuring the best possible outcome for the client is everything. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When working with timber, there are a huge range of species to choose from -  and they are all unique in terms of how they respond to their environment. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is not just the architects job to specify the right timber so that it looks great when first installed - it is their job to make sure the timber will look great for a lifetime. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating ensures timber is protected from day one and beyond. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Sydney Timber Solutions, our product of choice is Cutek, and that\'s for a few few reasons. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cute oil is unique in that it penetrates deep beneath the timber surface to protect from within. You can read more about this here. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cutek is proudly Australian manufactured and owned. They know our countries conditions, and have developed a product that responds to this. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They also offer an extensive range of colourtones, so whatever the style, there will be a colourtone to suit. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '177-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-30 02:52:36', '2019-04-30 02:52:36', '', 177, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/177-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
