(213, 1, '2019-05-08 04:24:12', '2019-05-08 04:24:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Timber Merchants </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, pre-coating is a no brainer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your timber arrives onsite and pre-treated with the chosen application already applied.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When timber is pre-coated, all six sides of the timber are treated  which means the timber is fully protected from day one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coated timber also means youre saving valuable time during the building process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once pre-coated, timber can be installed straight away. And if your timber is sitting onsite for a while, you can rest easy knowing that it is protected from the elements.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Put simply, when your timber arrives pre-coated, its one less thing you have to worry about.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Building & Construction', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '183-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-05-08 04:24:12', '2019-05-08 04:24:12', '', 183, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
