dge continues to be a source of pride for the local community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Project | Yandhai Nepean Crossing, Penrith', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '252-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-05-24 06:04:04', '2019-05-24 06:04:04', '', 252, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/252-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
