 Member for Penrith. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The new bridge continues to be a source of pride for the local community.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p><!--EndFragment--></p>', 'Yandhai Nepean Crossing, Penrith', 'The Yandhai Nepean Crossing is a new pedestrian and cyclist bridge that spans the Nepean River between Penrith and Emu Plains. It was officially opened in October 2018. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '268-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-04 01:59:38', '2019-06-04 01:59:38', '', 268, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/268-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
