(295, 2, '2019-06-08 10:34:05', '2019-06-08 10:34:05', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This building was originally a series of terraces that were converted into one large commercial premise. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>During construction phase much of the timber was exposed. The chosen timber (laminated beams) was never intended to be subject to external weather conditions, however due to the time lapse between initial construction and the roof finally going on, the timber had weathered significantly. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For this project, all of the timber was thoroughly sanded, and then coated with Cutek Extreme. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":302} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Elizabeth-St-Paddington-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-302\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":296} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Elizabeth-St-Paddington-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-296\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":297} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Elizabeth-St-Paddington-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-297\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":299} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Elizabeth-St-Paddington-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-299\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":301} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Elizabeth-St-Paddington-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-301\"/></figure