(322, 2, '2019-06-10 05:21:46', '2019-06-10 05:21:46', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber on site, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-coating protects timber from...</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Moisture</li><li>Cupping</li><li>Warping</li><li>Splitting</li><li>Checking</li><li>Rot</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is <a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\">Cutek</a> - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, <a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\">Cutek</a> works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides ongoing protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch this short video that explains \'The Cutek Difference\' and how it works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/what-is-the-cutek-difference/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\' (opens in a new tab)\">Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\'</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 05:21:46', '2019-06-10 05:21:46', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(323, 2, '2019-06-10 05:22:58', '2019-06-10 05:22:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber on site, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-coating protects timber from...</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Moisture</li><li>Cupping</li><li>Warping</li><li>Splitting</li><li>Checking</li><li>Rot</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is <a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a> - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, <a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a> works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides ongoing protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch this short video that explains \'The Cutek Difference\' and how it works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\' (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/what-is-the-cutek-difference/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\'</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 05:22:58', '2019-06-10 05:22:58', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(324, 2, '2019-06-10 05:25:44', '2019-06-10 05:25:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Sydney Timber Solutions we are experts in rejuvenating timber decking, cladding and any other external timber surface. Preparation is key, so much of our emphasis is on preparing the surfaces to ensure a great result. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Typically, our process involves:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Cleaning</strong><br>Prior to any application, it is essential that the timber has been cleaned. Our team of professionals will thoroughly clean your timber surfaces to ensure a perfect end result.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Sanding</strong><br>Where sanding is required, we use an industrial strength vacuum system to ensure dust is virtually eliminated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Oiling &amp; Staining</strong><br>Once the timber surfaces have been prepared, we apply your chosen finishes. Whilst we have worked with many brands over the years, our product of choice is <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\">Cutek</a></strong>. To find out more, <strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"click here (opens in a new tab)\">click here</a></strong>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Upon completion</strong><br>We do a complete clean and clear so youre ready to once again enjoy the beautiful rejuvenated look of your timber.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong> </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Due to a large number of current projects, we are not taking on any new residential restoration or maintenance work. If your requirements are not urgent or you still wish to enquire, please get in touch using the <a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/contact/\"><strong>Contact Us</strong></a> form.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Restoration & Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 05:25:44', '2019-06-10 05:25:44', '', 95, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(325, 2, '2019-06-10 05:26:54', '2019-06-10 05:26:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber on site, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-coating protects timber from...</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Moisture</li><li>Cupping</li><li>Warping</li><li>Splitting</li><li>Checking</li><li>Rot</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\">Cutek</a></strong> - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, <strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\">Cutek</a></strong> works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides ongoing protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch this short video that explains \'The Cutek Difference\' and how it works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\' (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/what-is-the-cutek-difference/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\'</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 05:26:54', '2019-06-10 05:26:54', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(327, 2, '2019-06-10 05:38:02', '2019-06-10 05:38:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> For architects, ensuring the best possible outcome for the client is everything. When working with timber, there are a huge range of species to choose from, and they are all unique in terms of how they respond to their environment. It is not just the architects job to specify the right timber so that it looks great when first installed - it is their job to make sure the timber will look great for a lifetime. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating ensures timber is protected from day one and beyond. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Sydney Timber Solutions, our product of choice is Cutek, and that\'s for a few few reasons. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Cutek oil is unique in that it penetrates deep beneath the timber surface to protect from within. This video explains \'The Cutek Difference\' and why it is the superior choice for protecting timber.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Cutek is 100% Australian manufactured and owned. They know our countries conditions, and have developed a product that responds to it. </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Cutek offer an extensive range of colourtones, so whatever the style, there will be a colourtone to suit. <br><br><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"View Cutek Colourtones (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/product/colourtones/\" target=\"_blank\">View Cutek Colourtones</a></strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '177-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 05:38:02', '2019-06-10 05:38:02', '', 177, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/177-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(328, 2, '2019-06-10 06:35:32', '2019-06-10 06:35:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is Cutek, and here\'s why.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When we first started in the restoration and maintenance business, we came across, and used, a broad range of timber finishes. Some would look great when initially done, but would soon deteriorate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whilst the deterioration didn\'t look good, the bigger issue was that the timber was now exposed to the elements. And once this happens, the timber becomes susceptible to issues such as cracking, splitting, warping and rotting. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Unlike other coatings that traditionally sit on the surface of the timber, Cutek is different in that it penetrates deeply into the timber to protect it from the inside out. Because of this, the timber stays better protected for longer in all weather conditions. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>\'The Cutek Difference\'</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch this short video that simply explains how Cutek works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/what-is-the-cutek-difference/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\' (opens in a new tab)\">Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\'</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Cutek', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '310-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-06-10 06:35:32', '2019-06-10 06:35:32', '', 310, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/310-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
