(347, 2, '2019-06-11 01:04:59', '2019-06-11 01:04:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether it\'s planning a new structure, or arranging a refresh for an existing structure, Councils have the tricky job of ensuring an end result that meets practical requirements, is cost effective and looks great.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sydney Timber Solutions have been engaged on numerous council based projects to restore and maintain timber structures including public buildings, public walkways, and train stations. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve also pre-coated large volumes of timber, so that it arrived pre-treated and protected prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/restoration-maintenance/\">Read more about our restoration and maintenance services</a></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\">Read more about our pre-coating services</a></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>View some of our<a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/our-work/\"> <strong>feature projects</strong></a>, including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":257,\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_9480-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-257\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/project/the-connection-rhodes/\" target=\"_blank\">The Connection, Rhodes</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":238,\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Penrith-Bridge-3-e1558672674812-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-238\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/project/project-yandhai-nepean-crossing-penrith/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Yandhai Nepean Crossing, Penrith</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Council', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '181-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-11 01:04:59', '2019-06-11 01:04:59', '', 181, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/181-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(348, 2, '2019-06-11 01:07:55', '2019-06-11 01:07:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is where timber is treated with your specified application, prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Why pre-coat?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating is a great way of ensuring that all sides of your timber are treated and protected prior to use. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Particularly for decking where moisture can be problematic, pre-coating provides an added level of protection for your (or your customers) investment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, having the timber arrive onsite pre-treated, means it is protected from day one. It also means you\'re not wasting time or resources treating timber on site, or cleaning up the aftermath.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Pre-coating protects timber from...</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Moisture</li><li>Cupping</li><li>Warping</li><li>Splitting</li><li>Checking</li><li>Rot</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How does pre-coating work?</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pieces of timber are fed through our pre-coating machine where your chosen application is first sprayed, before going through a series of brushes to ensure the coating is evenly dispersed. It is then stacked to allow absorption and diffusion.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Product of choice</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our product of choice is <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\">Cutek</a></strong> - a leader in the wood coating market. Unlike other coatings, <strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\">Cutek</a></strong> works by diffusing deeply into the timber, rather than sitting on the surface. This unique penetrating oil provides ongoing protection from moisture and offers hassle-free maintenance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch this short video that explains \'The Cutek Difference\' and how it works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/JK0ENtp5__k\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\' (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.cutek.com.au/what-is-the-cutek-difference/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about \'The Cutek Difference\'</a></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pre-Coating', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-11 01:07:55', '2019-06-11 01:07:55', '', 93, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(349, 2, '2019-06-11 01:12:43', '2019-06-11 01:12:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are in the business of protecting timber and bringing out its natural beauty. So we work with people that care about this too. That includes;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Architects (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/architects/\" target=\"_blank\">Architects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Builders (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/building-construction/\" target=\"_blank\">Builders</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/council/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Councils and Government (opens in a new tab)\">Councils and Government</a></strong></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Commercial Businesses (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/commercial/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Commercial Businesses</strong></a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Residential / Home Owners (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/residential/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Residential / Home Owners</strong></a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Timber Merchants (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/timber-merchants/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Timber Merchants</strong></a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Who we work with', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-11 01:12:43', '2019-06-11 01:12:43', '', 88, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
