(371, 2, '2019-06-11 03:29:06', '2019-06-11 03:29:06', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For building and construction, pre-coating is a no brainer. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your timber arrives onsite and pre-treated with the chosen application already applied.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When timber is pre-coated, all six sides of the timber are treated - which means the timber is fully protected from day one. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coated timber also means youre saving valuable time during the building process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once pre-coated, timber can be installed straight away. And if your timber is sitting onsite for a while, you can rest easy knowing that it is protected from the elements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Put simply, when your timber arrives pre-coated, its one less thing you have to worry about.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Read more about our restoration and maintenance services (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/restoration-maintenance/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more about our restoration and maintenance services</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Read more about our pre-coating services (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more about our pre-coating services</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"View our feature projects (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/category/projects/\" target=\"_blank\">View our feature projects</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Builders', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-11 03:29:06', '2019-06-11 03:29:06', '', 147, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(372, 2, '2019-06-11 03:29:17', '2019-06-11 03:29:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether it\'s planning a new structure, or arranging a refresh for an existing structure, Councils have the tricky job of ensuring an end result that meets practical requirements, is cost effective and looks great.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sydney Timber Solutions have been engaged on numerous council based projects to restore and maintain timber structures including public buildings, public walkways, and train stations. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve also pre-coated large volumes of timber, so that it arrived pre-treated and protected prior to installation. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Read more about our restoration and maintenance services (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/restoration-maintenance/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more about our restoration and maintenance services</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Read more about our pre-coating services (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more about our pre-coating services</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"View our feature projects (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/category/projects/\" target=\"_blank\">View our feature projects</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":257,\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/IMG_9480-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-257\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media