(380, 2, '2019-06-11 04:37:18', '2019-06-11 04:37:18', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Connection is acommunity facility located on the Rhodes foreshore. It caters for a wide range of events and requirements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This facility was originally <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>pre-coated</strong></a> using <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a> so this was purely a maintenance job to freshen up the timber cladding on the buildings as well as the timber decks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All timber surfaces were washed thoroughly using Cutek Proclean and then coated with Cutek Extreme, using a Sela Brown colourtone. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This maintenance job was a simple process due to the initial investment in <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"pre-coating (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>pre-coating</strong></a> the timber and using <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'The Connection, Rhodes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '340-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-11 04:37:18', '2019-06-11 04:37:18', '', 340, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/340-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
