(390, 2, '2019-06-11 05:28:13', '2019-06-11 05:28:13', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Connection is a&nbsp;community facility located on the Rhodes foreshore. It caters for a wide range of functions and events.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This facility was originally <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>pre-coated</strong></a> using <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a> so this was purely a maintenance job to freshen up the timber cladding on the buildings as well as the timber decks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All timber surfaces were washed thoroughly using Cutek Proclean and then coated with Cutek Extreme, using a Sela Brown colourtone. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This maintenance job was a simple process due to the initial investment in <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"pre-coating (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/pre-coating/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>pre-coating</strong></a> the timber and using <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cutek (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/cutek/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cutek</strong></a>. &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":385} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/The-Connection-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/><figcaption>One of the Connection buildings, prior to maintenance.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":384} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/The-Connection-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-384\"/><figcaption>The same area after we had cleaned and applied Cutek o