(419, 1, '2019-06-17 23:56:49', '2019-06-17 23:56:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For architects, ensuring the best possible outcome for the client is everything.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When working with timber, there are a huge range of species to choose from, and they are all unique in terms of how they respond to their environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is not just the architects job to specify the right timber so that it looks great when first installed  it is their job to make sure the timber will look great for a lifetime.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pre-coating ensures timber is protected from day one and beyond.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Sydney Timber Solutions, our product of choice is Cutek, and thats for a few reasons.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Architects', 'For architects, ensuring the best possible outcome for the client is everything.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '399-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-17 23:56:49', '2019-06-17 23:56:49', '', 399, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/399-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(420, 1, '2019-06-17 23:57:01', '2019-06-17 23:57:01', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nWhether its planning a new structure, or arranging a refresh for an existing structure, Councils have the sometimes challenging job of ensuring an end result that meets practical requirements, is cost effective and looks great.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Councils', 'Whether its planning a new structure, or arranging a refresh for an existing structure', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '402-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-17 23:57:01', '2019-06-17 23:57:01', '', 402, 'https://sydneytimbersolutions.com.au/402-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
